title: The Maid
writer: Sebastián Silva (story), Sebastián Silva, Pedro Peirano
actors: Catalina Saavedra, Claudia Celedón, Mariana Loyola, Andrea García-Huidobro
plot: The story of how a maid called Raquel, who has worked for over 20 years in one affluent Chilean household, rediscovers herself. La Nana is a microcosm of Latin social hierarchy while also focusing on one woman's journey to free herself from a mental servitude of her own making
awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 34 wins & 21 nominations.
